WEBVTT

00:03:58.072 --> 00:04:00.771
down to less than a few days.

00:04:00.795 --> 00:04:04.540
So began a "polite"
competition for resources.

00:04:05.408 --> 00:04:08.202
OK, let me not mince words.
It was a fierce battle.

00:04:08.226 --> 00:04:09.994
We dropped everything,

00:04:10.018 --> 00:04:11.464
working around the clock,

00:04:11.488 --> 00:04:15.369
trying to craft
perfectly crafted proposal words

00:04:15.393 --> 00:04:17.638
to send to the observatory directors.

00:04:18.527 --> 00:04:21.375
Well, good news. We got the time.

00:04:22.178 --> 00:04:25.741
Now, from a perfectly
selfish point of view,

00:04:25.765 --> 00:04:30.131
the first thing we might like to know
is how massive 'Oumuamua is.